    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "About the purpose of the widget: what does it means to have a \"free shipping\" toggle?\n- when on: show me only the free shipping items\n- when off: show me both free and not free shipping\n\nThe thing is that for some other properties it may not be what the user wants to express.\nIf I have an `archive` boolean attribute for my store, does the toggle means:\n- when on: show me only the archived items\n- when off: show me only the active (non archived) items\n\nOr does it means:\n- when on: show me only the archived items\n- when off: show me both\n",
    "created_at": "2015-08-06T14:00:44Z",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/41#issuecomment-128375498",
