    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I'm not yet sold on the switch or toggle naming. We are not really switching from true to false, we are switching from true to undefined.\n\nThe name does not really reflect that and will lead to confusion. Maybe `restrictToggle` or `restrictSwitch` instead.\n",
